    <section class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Achille</h2>
        <p>You probably know me and if you don't here is <a href="https://achilleme.com/">my website</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Email privacy</h2>
        <p>Only an hash of the email address is stored in the PhysCraft database. The hash is stored just to prevent abuses of the system and cannot be used in anyway to get your email address back. So don't worry about spam or anything &lt3.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Hosting and APIs</h2>
        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">The webserver and database are hosted on my own server: <a
                        href="https://achilleme.com/bifrost.html">Bifrost</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6d/Flag_of_Amsterdam.svg/2560px-Flag_of_Amsterdam.svg.png" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">The Minecraft server is hosted by <a href="https://pebblehost.com/">Pebblehost</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://pebblehost.com/src/img/logos/p.png" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">The server used is <a href="https://maileroo.com/">Fabric</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://fabricmc.net/assets/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">Email are handled by <a href="https://maileroo.com/">Maileroo</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://cdn.maileroo.com/branding/logo_orange_icon.svg" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">Donations are handled by <a href="https://maileroo.com/">PayPal</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/paypal-ui/logos/svg/paypal-mark-color.svg" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <p class="mb-0">Domains and other stuff are handled by <a href="https://maileroo.com/">Cloudflare</a>.</p>
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/94/Cloudflare_Logo.png" alt="Logo" class="mr-3"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Open source</h2>
        <p>Most of the code that is used to run this service is open source, here are some link:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/PhysCraft/webserver">PhysCraft/webserver</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/PhysCraft/backups">PhysCraft/backups</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/FabricMC">FabricMC</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

